    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="bpl.00015.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden<ptr target="bpl.00015_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1887-07-01">July 1 2&#189;P M</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Yours of yesterday rec'd&#8212;Yes I would get along handsomely with 800&#8212;(have
                already rec'd nearly half that from S B).<ptr target="n6000"/></p> 
            
            <p>&#8212;A hot spell here, &#38; I am feeling it&#8212;H G.<ptr target="n0262"/> is here
                    painting&#8212;Morse<ptr target="n0862"/> is here&#8212;I shall send you the
                copy of S D<ptr target="bpl.00015_n2"/> soon&#8212;Have just had my dinner of boiled
                mutton &#38; new potatoes&#8212;good&#8212;O how the sun glares&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="bpl.00015.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
